                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.674/36: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the High
                        Commissioner at Constantinople</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bristol</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-01-10T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 10, 1924—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>9. Your telegram 340 of December 31. Your recommendation approved. You should
                    keep in mind, however, that the question is one in which a large body of our
                    citizens is interested directly or indirectly. It would be desirable if
                    possible, therefore, for you to arrange the <hi rend="italic">modus vivendi</hi>
                    to which you referred in your final sentence.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
